    "content": "<p>首先打开修改工具找到路径<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><code>ui/skill/skillshopwindow.ui</code></span><br />\n首先发现我玩的版本这里X轴和Y轴被改成999了也就是到视界外面去了找一个有这个按钮的版本将参数复制过来<br />\n<img alt=\"\" height=\"489\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/22/image-20230722154046-1.png\" width=\"900\" /><br />\n下面那个&ldquo;初始化&rdquo;是和按钮上显示的字挂钩的，龙鸣60字太多了都超出UI了所以改回来了<br />\n上面的<code><span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">1000</span></code>按钮对应下图的3，<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><code>1001&nbsp;</code><code>1002&nbsp;</code><code>1003</code></span>对应下图的2<img alt=\"\" height=\"670\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/22/image-20230722154100-2.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>关于SP改回，修改工具<code><span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">skillshopwindow.ui</span></code>往下翻找到有<code><span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">[numberset]</span></code>的节点图片SP.img和TP.img已经说明是那个节点了。</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"481\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/22/image-20230722154116-3.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>比如龙鸣60的是<code><span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">SP01.img</span></code>,找到对应的NPK文件确认，没有这个样式就找个找个自己喜欢的样式换掉<img alt=\"\" height=\"694\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/22/image-20230722154130-4.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>改好后SP就显示了</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"672\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/22/image-20230722154154-5.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>然后精调一下X轴和Y轴​​​​​​​<img alt=\"\" height=\"490\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/22/image-20230722154208-6.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>调整好后完工，登入游戏就和图2一样了。</p>\n",
